892
00:58:48,630 --> 00:58:49,964
I need to see the records

893
00:58:50,006 --> 00:58:51,716
for a patient named Anna Morgan.

894
00:58:51,758 --> 00:58:54,260
Are you a relative?

895
00:58:54,260 --> 00:58:55,595
Well, no.

896
00:58:55,595 --> 00:58:56,721
