899
00:58:59,933 --> 00:59:01,768
Well, she's been dead 24 years.

900
00:59:01,768 --> 00:59:03,269
I don't think she'll mind.

901
00:59:03,311 --> 00:59:04,604
I'm sorry.

902
00:59:04,646 --> 00:59:06,564
It's impossible.

903
00:59:06,606 --> 00:59:08,566
Look...

904
00:59:08,608 --> 00:59:10,777
I've seen them before.

905
00:59:10,818 --> 00:59:12,362
I've been up there.

906
00:59:12,403 --> 00:59:13,446
MAN:
Nice try.

907
00:59:13,488 --> 00:59:16,115
The record rooms
are downstairs, guy.

908
00:59:16,157 --> 00:59:18,159
