1004
01:06:24,711 --> 01:06:25,837
(whispering):
Anna.

1005
01:06:30,717 --> 01:06:33,011
"Anna Morgan's...

1006
01:06:33,052 --> 01:06:35,597
...Hallucinations"?

1007
01:06:35,722 --> 01:06:37,557
What's wrong with you?

1008
01:06:42,186 --> 01:06:44,480
"'65, conceived."

1009
01:06:44,522 --> 01:06:45,898
"'65, miscarriage."

1010
01:06:45,940 --> 01:06:47,483
"'66, conceived."

1011
01:06:47,525 --> 01:06:49,235
"'66, miscarriage."

1012
01:06:49,277 --> 01:06:52,113
Christ, she wouldn't give up.

1013
01:06:55,950 --> 01:06:58,494
