1015
01:07:23,061 --> 01:07:27,941
"Sessions terminated...
at father's request.

1016
01:07:27,982 --> 01:07:31,903
See Video Record S-M-0-1-5."

1017
01:07:31,945 --> 01:07:34,072
(phone ringing)

1018
01:07:34,113 --> 01:07:37,075
(grinding furiously)

1019
01:07:40,787 --> 01:07:42,789
RUTH:
Aidan?

1020
01:07:42,789 --> 01:07:44,791
Aidan, it's your mom.

1021
01:07:52,799 --> 01:07:54,801
(Aidan over telephone):
Hi, Mom.

1022
01:07:54,801 --> 01:07:56,928
Honey, the house you drew
for me...

1023
01:07:56,970 --> 01:07:57,971
Uh-huh?

1024
01:07:57,971 --> 01:07:59,389
...where did you see it?

1025
01:07:59,430 --> 01:08:01,099
Did you see it in your head?

1026
01:08:01,140 --> 01:08:02,684
Is that why you drew it?

1027
01:08:02,809 --> 01:08:04,143
In my head?

1028
01:08:04,143 --> 01:08:06,980
Aidan... why did you draw
that house?

1029
01:08:06,980 --> 01:08:08,690
Because she told me to.

1030
01:08:08,815 --> 01:08:09,983
Who?

1031
01:08:10,024 --> 01:08:13,194
Who told you to?

1032
01:08:13,236 --> 01:08:14,904
The little girl.

1033
01:08:18,324 --> 01:08:21,828
She talks to you?

1034
01:08:21,869 --> 01:08:23,830
No.

1035
01:08:23,871 --> 01:08:25,832
She shows me things.

1036
01:08:25,873 --> 01:08:28,459
Did she show you the horses?

1037
01:08:28,501 --> 01:08:31,629
She doesn't like it in the barn.

1038
01:08:31,671 --> 01:08:34,841
The horses keep her up at night.

1039
01:08:34,882 --> 01:08:38,469
So, she still lives there?

1040
01:08:40,555 --> 01:08:43,016
No.

1041
01:08:43,016 --> 01:08:46,227
(whispering):
She lives in a dark place now.

1042
01:08:54,652 --> 01:08:56,154
(clock ticking)

1043
01:09:02,827 --> 01:09:06,164
(puzzle pieces clicking)

1044
01:09:06,205 --> 01:09:08,166
(ticking loudly)

1045
01:09:08,207 --> 01:09:10,209
(puzzle pieces clicking)

1046
01:09:11,377 --> 01:09:12,503
(door opening)

1047
01:09:12,545 --> 01:09:14,005
WOMAN:
You're getting a little old

1048
01:09:14,047 --> 01:09:15,757
to be crabbing out there, Cal.

1049
01:09:15,798 --> 01:09:17,967
Your body's about outlived
its warranty, you know.

1050
01:09:18,009 --> 01:09:19,969
You ain't exactly
the catch of the day.

1051
01:09:20,011 --> 01:09:22,722
Oh... let's see you
catch one better!

1052
01:09:22,764 --> 01:09:23,723
CAL:
Yeah...

1053
01:09:23,765 --> 01:09:25,725
Good afternoon.

1054
01:09:25,767 --> 01:09:27,727
I'm Dr. Grasnik.

1055
01:09:27,769 --> 01:09:29,729
I think he was here before me.

1056
01:09:29,771 --> 01:09:32,732
Darby? Darby's always here.

1057
01:09:32,774 --> 01:09:34,734
Aren't you, Darby?

1058
01:09:34,776 --> 01:09:36,361
He's my son's boy.

1059
01:09:36,402 --> 01:09:39,072
Come over on the ferry, did you?

1060
01:09:39,113 --> 01:09:40,573
Yes.

1061
01:09:40,615 --> 01:09:44,285
Um... have you lived here long?

1062
01:09:44,327 --> 01:09:45,286
Born and raised.

1063
01:09:45,328 --> 01:09:46,913
Only doctor on the island.

1064
01:09:46,955 --> 01:09:50,583
Then you know the Morgans
and their daughter.

1065
01:09:50,625 --> 01:09:53,169
Do you know
their daughter?

1066
01:09:53,211 --> 01:09:55,755
Do you know their daughter?

1067
01:09:55,797 --> 01:09:57,423
(clock ticking continuing)

1068
01:09:57,465 --> 01:09:58,758
What's this about?

1069
01:09:58,800 --> 01:10:00,426
Look, I'm sorry.

1070
01:10:00,468 --> 01:10:02,804
L-I don't know how to say this

1071
01:10:02,887 --> 01:10:06,349
but I'm seeing things
in my head... images...

1072
01:10:06,391 --> 01:10:08,351
and so is my son.

1073
01:10:08,393 --> 01:10:11,980
My son, that...
that's why I'm here

1074
01:10:12,021 --> 01:10:15,817
and somehow,
I don't know how, but...

1075
01:10:15,858 --> 01:10:18,611
it's because of that girl.

1076
01:10:21,990 --> 01:10:25,535
Haven't heard anybody say that
in a long time.

1077
01:10:27,161 --> 01:10:28,454
(squeaking loudly)

1078
01:10:28,496 --> 01:10:30,957
She wanted a child
more than anything.

1079
01:10:30,957 --> 01:10:32,083
Poor Anna.

1080
01:10:32,125 --> 01:10:33,751
They tried hard for years

1081
01:10:33,793 --> 01:10:36,379
but sometimes
it's just not meant to be.

1082
01:10:36,421 --> 01:10:38,423
Then one winter, they went away.

1083
01:10:38,464 --> 01:10:39,757
When they came back

1084
01:10:39,799 --> 01:10:41,759
it was with Samara.

1085
01:10:41,801 --> 01:10:43,761
Adopted, they said.

1086
01:10:43,803 --> 01:10:45,722
Never did say from where.

1087
01:10:45,763 --> 01:10:49,142
Said the mother had died
of complications.

1088
01:10:49,183 --> 01:10:51,936
But they had their baby,
they had their horses...

1089
01:10:51,978 --> 01:10:53,980
everything was fine...

1090
01:10:54,022 --> 01:10:56,399
till Anna started coming
to see me.

1091
01:10:56,441 --> 01:10:58,610
Said she was
suffering visions...

1092
01:10:58,651 --> 01:10:59,986
seeing things...

1093
01:10:59,986 --> 01:11:01,988
horrible things...

1094
01:11:01,988 --> 01:11:04,782
like they'd been burned
inside her...

1095
01:11:04,824 --> 01:11:06,784
and it only happened

1096
01:11:06,826 --> 01:11:08,119
around Samara...

1097
01:11:08,161 --> 01:11:10,496
that the girl put them there.

1098
01:11:10,496 --> 01:11:12,498
(merry-go-round
squeaking continues)

1099
01:11:12,498 --> 01:11:15,501
Were you Samara's
doctor, too?

1100
01:11:15,501 --> 01:11:18,296
Was there anything wrong
with her?

1101
01:11:18,338 --> 01:11:19,797
You mean medically?

1102
01:11:19,839 --> 01:11:21,883
I mean whatever you mean.

1103
01:11:21,966 --> 01:11:24,302
(squeaking continuing)

1104
01:11:24,344 --> 01:11:27,805
When Darby, there, was born...

1105
01:11:27,847 --> 01:11:32,769
we knew something wasn't right
with him...

1106
01:11:32,810 --> 01:11:35,813
but we loved him anyway.

1107
01:11:35,855 --> 01:11:38,191
Takes work, you know.

1108
01:11:38,232 --> 01:11:40,985
Some people have limits.

1109
01:11:43,029 --> 01:11:45,865
So, what happened to her?

1110
01:11:45,907 --> 01:11:48,618
I referred them
to Eola Psychiatric

1111
01:11:48,660 --> 01:11:49,911
on the mainland.

1112
01:11:49,953 --> 01:11:51,996
I assume she's still there.

1113
01:11:52,038 --> 01:11:54,540
You don't know?

1114
01:11:54,540 --> 01:11:58,002
